        <!--TODO: productDef="LC-What is the product, service, or idea you're promoting?" v-->

        <section class="py-5" id="PRODUCT DEFINITION">
          <h2 class="pt-5">PRODUCT DEFINITION</h2>
          <p class="">
            CREATE LONGER VERSION:::: 1st paragraph, elaborate and explanation
            of lc/ Core Idea: Position your service as a digital atelier—a
            creative studio where your clients' visions are translated into
            vivid, handcrafted websites. Think of each site as a collaborative
            artwork: your client brings the inspiration, and you bring the
            technical brushstrokes "What separates web developers from Ai? Human
            innovation!
          </p>
          <p>
            Most web design services focus on tech, speed, or business
            optimization. Few lean into artisanal design, emotional
            storytelling, and cozy aesthetics the way this concept (lc) does.
          </p>
        </section>
        <img
