          <h2>Key Features/Offers:</h2>
          <ul class="bg-">
            <li>
              Portfolio-First Design: Build sites that feel like immersive
              galleries or journals.
            </li>
            <li>
              Storytelling Frameworks: Let creatives tell their brand story
              visually and emotionally.
            </li>
            <li>
              Creative Companion Calls: A process that feels more like an artist
              collaboration than a business transaction.
            </li>
            <li>
              “Palette Picker” Questionnaire: Help clients choose colors based
              on their work and style.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

